    "updated_at": "2024-12-10T12:35:47Z",
    "body": "`winget install --scope machine --exact --id Starship.Starship`\r\n\r\nworks perfectly now but\r\n\r\n`winget install --scope user --exact --id Starship.Starship`\r\n\r\ninstalls starship to C:\\Program Files\\starship instead of %LOCALAPPDATA%\\Programs\\starship\r\n\r\n```yaml\r\nPackageIdentifier: Starship.Starship\r\nPackageVersion: 1.21.1\r\nInstallerLocale: en-US\r\nMinimumOSVersion: 10.0.0.0\r\nInstallers:\r\n- Architecture: x64\r\n  InstallerType: wix\r\n  Scope: machine\r\n  InstallerUrl: https://github.com/starship/starship/releases/download/v1.21.1/starship-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.msi\r\n  InstallerSha256: 90620DF005C45AC000EF301C980239087E787A74AE92651E7C1B0F2CDC0B5BC6\r\n  ProductCode: '{BBB12985-822B-45F1-9AF3-CF85C368763E}'\r\n- Architecture: x64\r\n  InstallerType: wix\r\n  Scope: user\r\n  InstallerUrl: https://github.com/starship/starship/releases/download/v1.21.1/starship-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.msi\r\n  InstallerSha256: 90620DF005C45AC000EF301C980239087E787A74AE92651E7C1B0F2CDC0B5BC6\r\n  ProductCode: '{BBB12985-822B-45F1-9AF3-CF85C368763E}'\r\n  InstallerSwitches:\r\n    Custom: ALLUSERS=2 MSIINSTALLPERUSER=1\r\n```\r\nperhaps installerswitches could fix that problem\r\n\r\nhttps://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/msi/allusers\r\nhttps://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/msi/msiinstallperuser\r\n",
